GitHub Workflow Structure

Under Repository
Workflow1
    -> Job (Runners) Build/Test Jobs...each Job we have multiple steps
    -> 
WorkFlow2
    -> Job (Runners) Build/Test Jobs...each Job we have multiple steps
    -> 

Goto Actions
Configure-> Simple Workflow

.github/workflows/blank.yaml or yml
****************************************************************************
name: Hello World
#Triggers are configured under 
on: workflow_dispatch
jobs: 
  #provide name of the job
  dbtjob:
      runs-on: ubuntu-latest #runners
      steps:
        - name: Hello Step
          run: echo "Welcome to Github Actions"







